{"opinion":{"isContribuable":false,"votes_total":11,"arguments_yes_count":0,"arguments_no_count":0,"id":354,"created_at":"2015-09-30T14:26:43+0200","updated_at":"2015-09-30T14:27:55+0200","body":"<p>Les &eacute;diteurs qui souhaitent utiliser les services de publicit&eacute;s en ligne cibl&eacute;es vendues par Google, Criteo, RocketFuel, etc... pour mon&eacute;tiser leurs espaces devront proposer obligatoirement&nbsp;une fen&ecirc;tre (popup window) de validation pour ent&eacute;riner le choix de&nbsp;l&#39;internaute qui&nbsp;accepte ou non de recevoir ce type de publicit&eacute; qui est propos&eacute;e dans les formats courants, textes, banni&egrave;res, images et vid&eacute;os.&nbsp;<\/p>","versions_count":0,"sources_count":0,"arguments_count":0,"author":{"username":"Pascal Rossini","displayName":"Pascal Rossini","uniqueId":"pascalrossini","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/pascalrossini","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}},"type":{"id":97,"title":"Section 4","subtitle":"Information des consommateurs","voteWidgetType":2,"votesHelpText":"Pensez-vous que cette proposition permet d'atteindre les objectifs pr\u00e9sent\u00e9s dans l\u2019explication de l\u2019article ?","commentSystem":2,"color":"blue","versionable":true,"sourceable":true,"votesThreshold":null,"votesThresholdHelpText":null},"sources":[],"arguments":[],"modals":[],"votes":[{"user":{"username":"Superchaton","displayName":"Superchaton","uniqueId":"superchaton","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/superchaton","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/edit-profile"}}},{"user":{"username":"Bonin","displayName":"Bonin","uniqueId":"bonin","isAdmin":false,"media":null,"vip":false,"_links":{"profile":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/profile\/bonin","settings":"https:\/\/www.republique-numerique.fr\/